# Card Highlight debug

- **`/debug`** builds diagnostics server-side (`getCardHighlightImageDebugPayload` / `getCardTraderJinaDebugPayload`); **`GET /api/debug/*`** returns the same JSON (no env flag required).
- User can run **`npm run debug:card`** (with `npm run dev` on `localhost:3000`, or `SITE_URL=https://… npm run debug:card` for production).
- That writes **`last-card-debug.json`** at repo root (gitignored) and prints the same JSON to stdout.
- When the user asks what the card debug says or to interpret it, **read `last-card-debug.json`** if it exists; otherwise ask them to run `npm run debug:card` or open `/debug` and retry.
